# NSQL Natural Language Pattern Examples

# Imperative Queries
show sales by region
show monthly revenue by product category for last quarter
show customer count by acquisition channel and signup date

# Calculation Queries
calculate average order value for premium customers
calculate churn rate for Q1 2025
calculate conversion rate by marketing channel

# Comparative Queries
compare this year vs last year by monthly sales
compare US vs Canada by customer retention rate
compare weekend vs weekday by order volume and average basket size

# Ranking Queries
find top 10 products by revenue
find top 5 customers by lifetime value for each region
find bottom 20 SKUs by inventory turnover

# Complex Natural Language Queries
show year-over-year growth by product category for North America
calculate customer lifetime value segmented by acquisition source
find products with reorder rate above category average